DISCLAIMER — TRADING RISK
=========================
This software trades real funds on Hyperliquid. Cryptocurrency trading is
highly speculative and can result in total loss of capital. The authors make
no representations about the profitability, fitness for purpose, or safety
of this software. You are solely responsible for any financial outcomes from
using or modifying this code. By using this software you acknowledge that:

  - The strategy may lose money.
  - Smart-contract risk on Hyperliquid is real (L1 propriétaire).
  - Bridge delays and smart-contract bugs can cause loss of funds.
  - You should never deploy more capital than you can afford to lose 100%.
  - Backtest results are not predictive of future performance.

Use at your own risk.
